Package: segmantR
Title: Cell Segmentation of Histology Slides with Human-in-the-Loop Training
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("R.", "Heller", , "raban.heller@charite.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8006-9742"))
Description: Comprehensive cell segmentation for histology and multiplexed
    tissue imaging. Provides classical segmentation methods (adaptive
    thresholding, watershed, Voronoi propagation), deep learning wrappers
    (Cellpose, StarDist, Mesmer via reticulate), and a human-in-the-loop
    iterative refinement workflow. A polished Shiny application lets
    researchers annotate, correct, train, evaluate, and download custom
    segmentation models without leaving R.
